		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">建造机关使用右侧机械臂对玩家发射一枚小型导弹，造成<span color="#b9b9b9">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">建造机关使用两个机械臂敲击地面，造成<span color="#b9b9b9">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">建造机关使用锯齿机械臂，并不断旋转自身，持续造成<span color="#ff9999">100%,20%,10%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">建造机关纵劈锯齿，利用滚动的锯齿向前不断移动，接触造成<span color="#ff9999">50%,10%,5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1119" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">建造机关在闲置时，会挖出地面的石块并将其运送至后方，落下的石块会造成<span color="#b8b8b8">10%</span><span>伤害；有20%的概率会挖出火史莱姆，史莱姆落下造成</span><span color="#ff9999">10%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">建造机关利用钩爪机械臂长时间不断对玩家发射低伤害的冰锥，冰锥造成<span color="#99ffff">10%,5%,2.5%,1%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="895" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">建造机关利用钩爪抓起冰块，旋转一圈，造成<span color="#99ffff">70%</span><span>伤害，然后顺势砸下，造成</span><span color="#99ffff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">建造机关使用锯齿进行一次纵向劈，并立即收回，纵劈与收回分别造成<span color="#ff9999">60%,40%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
